column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid,    p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, petroMag_i,    p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i,    p.petroR5#_g, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR5#_i,    p.petroR5#Err_g, p.petroR5#Err_r, p.petroR5#Err_i,    p.petroR9#_g, p.petroR9#_r, p.petroR9#_i,    p.petroR9#Err_g, p.petroR9#Err_r, p.petroR9#Err_i,   ISNULL(p.type, #) AS type,    ISNULL(s.z, #) AS z, ISNULL(s.zErr, #) AS zErr INTO mydb.hw1_short FROM Galaxy AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #   AND p.petroR5#Err_r < #   AND s.zConf > #
